@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

###

### Root — check model info
GET {{baseUrl}}/

###

### Single-turn chat — general question
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "What is a P/E ratio and why does it matter for investors?",
  "max_tokens": 512,
  "temperature": 0.7
}

###

### Single-turn chat — custom system prompt
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Summarise the key risks of investing in tech stocks right now.",
  "system_prompt": "You are a conservative investment advisor who always highlights downside risks first.",
  "max_tokens": 400,
  "temperature": 0.5
}

###

### Multi-turn chat — conversation with history
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat/multi-turn
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "messages": [
    { "role": "system",    "content": "You are a financial analyst assistant." },
    { "role": "user",      "content": "What is a P/E ratio?" },
    { "role": "assistant", "content": "A P/E ratio (Price-to-Earnings) compares a company's share price to its earnings per share. A high P/E may indicate growth expectations, while a low P/E can suggest undervaluation." },
    { "role": "user",      "content": "How does it compare to the P/B ratio?" }
  ],
  "max_tokens": 512,
  "temperature": 0.7
}

###

### Finance analysis — earnings data
POST {{baseUrl}}/analyse
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Q4 2024 results: Revenue $4.2B (up 12% YoY), Net Income $820M (up 8% YoY), Operating Margin 19.5%, Debt-to-Equity 1.4. Analyse this performance.",
  "max_tokens": 768
}

###

### Finance analysis — investment question
POST {{baseUrl}}/analyse
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "A business has a P/E of 35, revenue growth of 25% YoY, gross margin of 68%, and free cash flow of $200M on $1B revenue. Is this a good investment?",
  "max_tokens": 600
}

###

# ─── Document / RAG endpoints ────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Upload a PDF
# Change the file path to a real file on your machine
POST {{baseUrl}}/documents/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="report.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< /path/to/your/report.pdf
--boundary--

###

### Upload a CSV
POST {{baseUrl}}/documents/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="portfolio.csv"
Content-Type: text/csv

< /path/to/your/portfolio.csv
--boundary--

###

### Upload an Excel file
POST {{baseUrl}}/documents/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="financials.xlsx"
Content-Type: application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.spreadsheetml.sheet

< /path/to/your/financials.xlsx
--boundary--

###

### List all indexed documents
GET {{baseUrl}}/documents

###

### Ask a question about your uploaded documents (RAG)
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat/rag
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What was the total revenue mentioned in the documents?",
  "max_tokens": 512,
  "num_sources": 4
}

###

### Ask a finance-specific question about your documents
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat/rag
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What are the key risks mentioned across all the documents?",
  "max_tokens": 600,
  "num_sources": 5
}

###

### Clear all indexed documents
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/documents

